  <description><![CDATA[<p>The interconnected <a data-udi="umb://document/12973fa274f142b0ae87e912215cc2f5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/12973fa274f142b0ae87e912215cc2f5}" title="Sporthotel Strass">Sporthotel</a> &amp; Hotel Strass are two of the most popular hotels in <a data-udi="umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5}" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a>. Benefitting from an unbeatable location next to the main Penkenbahn lift in the heart of Mayrhofen's bustling centre.</p>
<h2>Lively après</h2>
<p>The hotel has a selection of lively in-house bars to choose from, including the Ice Bar, lounge with front of house terrace, and the adjacent Arena nightclub.</p>
<p>The shared facilities are excellent and include three indoor pools, a multi-floor spa centre, sizeable games room with pool and table tennis tables and children’s playroom.</p>
<p>All bedrooms are bright and spacious with homely pine furnishings.</p>
<h2>Spa area</h2>
<p>The 2000m² spa area features multiple types of sauna, an infrared cabin, steam room, inhalation grotto, multiple whirlpools, Kneipp pool, brine bath and various beauty and massage treatments. After a day on the slopes unwind in the fully-kitted out gym overlooking the town.</p>]]></description>
